We have to assign the option object to the value property instead of option.value. This is already identified by the reporter and fixed on their side hence closing this issue. Adding the updated code from @FromirDread for future reference.

```
const optionValue = {display: this.normalizeHyphens(this.translationService.instant(item.text))};
modusSelect.options.push(optionValue);

if(item.selected){
  this.value = optionValue;
}
```

